snippet.title: Trine: Ultimate Collection - Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
The Trine: Ultimate Collection, featuring Trine Enchanted Edition, Trine 2: Complete Story, Trine 3: Artifacts of Power, and Trine 4: The Nightmare Prince, will be out this fall for PC, Xbox One and PlayStation 4.

Watch more trailers here!
https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=vvB2wiDUDdA&list=PLaQokWZfgbynLRhV7HigqcfVAzsNB-t6b&index=1
